posts.post_content: My wife hails from Rochester, and she is very, very supportive of my collection.  I'd love to surprise her with a Rochester team set.  Questionable if she will care or not, but its the thought that counts.  Looking for PSA4 (or in the vicinity).  Let me know what you've got.

I only have a scan of one of my Ganzel's, but if you're interested then I can find the other one, and provide you with a scan of the one I'm offering.  E-mail works best for me.
